ZH: 我的姨妈每个月都会来。
EN: My aunt comes every month.

ZH: 姨妈对我很好，经常给我买礼物。
EN: My aunt is very nice to me, she often buys me presents.

ZH: 姨妈是我妈妈的妹妹。
EN: My aunt is my mom's sister.

ZH: 我的姨妈非常慷慨，总是帮助别人。
EN: My aunt is very generous, always helping others.

ZH: 星期六是我姨妈的生日，我们要一起庆祝。
EN: Saturday is my aunt's birthday, we are going to celebrate together.

ZH: 姨妈是我最亲近的亲戚之一。
EN: My aunt is one of my closest relatives.

ZH: 姨妈住在离我家很远的地方。
EN: My aunt lives far away from my house.

ZH: 我姨妈是一位护士，她每天都为他人照顾。
EN: My aunt is a nurse, she takes care of others every day.

ZH: 姨妈很爱干净，她每天都打扫整个房间。
EN: My aunt is very clean, she cleans the whole house every day.

ZH: 我姨妈很会做菜，每次我们去她家吃饭都非常美味。
EN: My aunt is a great cook, every time we eat at her place it's delicious.

ZH: 上个月，我跟我的姨妈一起去旅行了。
EN: Last month, I went on a trip with my aunt.

ZH: 我的姨妈是一名律师，她总是为我提供法律上的建议。
EN: My aunt is a lawyer, she always gives me legal advice.

ZH: 姨妈总是鼓励我努力学习。
EN: My aunt always encourages me to study hard.

ZH: 去年，我和我的姨妈一起去看了一场电影。
EN: Last year, I went to see a movie with my aunt.

ZH: 姨妈有一头漂亮的长发。
EN: My aunt has beautiful long hair.

ZH: 我的姨妈很善良，总是关心别人。
EN: My aunt is very kind, she always cares about others.

ZH: 每次姨妈来，我都会有不舒服的感觉。
EN: Every time my aunt comes, I feel uncomfortable.

ZH: 我的姨妈是一个非常有爱心的人。
EN: My aunt is a very caring person.

ZH: 姨妈跟我一样喜欢读书。
EN: My aunt likes reading just like me.

ZH: 我的姨妈总是给我很多鼓励。
EN: My aunt always gives me a lot of encouragement.
